        "action": "New scheme for all homes to be fitted with air conditioning",
        "additional_details": "We experience heatwaves in this country. I believe we are not used to them and cannot cope. Other countries have air conditioning in their homes and I think we should too, even if it\u2019s just the wall mounted ones in bedrooms and living rooms.",
        "background": "I think that with the heat we experience in our country, we should have air conditioning units fitted in homes. This could be supported by a government scheme so we pay off the cost each month, so it's like a bill.",
